narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Rwjbh Emergency Medicine Associates, LLC is a Nurse Practitioner, Primary Care provider based in Somerset, NJ. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $118.0M in Medicaid payments across 1.1M claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: This provider received $118.0M in taxpayer-funded Medicaid payments — enough to fund healthcare for approximately 14,745 Medicaid beneficiaries for a full year at average per-enrollee costs.
